						               													<description>Tales of Vespershard (ToV) is a miniatures skirmish game (32mm) with a fantasy aesthetic. It is based on the Uud universe, created by the Eldritch Foundry. The Vespersdhard represents the ability players have to shape their own universe.&amp;#10;We provide the story and a basic background. The players can use that to come up with any new adventure, story, and campaign, changing and adapting it totheir ideafor a fast and fun miniatures game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You want an elven-forged empire which has subdued all other races? Or do you want dragons easily upholding the plains? Or maybe for nightmares to come true at night and hunt down the unwary? Well, you can make all this a reality in ToV.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Many things are customizable at the rules level (scenery, campaigns, enemies ...), but you can also customize the miniatures for your gang thanks to the powerful Eldritch Foundry app, an indispensable collaborator for our project.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fight against your friends in dynamic battles between gangs, with a narrative touch and with heroes designed by you. Evolve your gang and link scenarios to create your own narrative campaign.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
